            "id": "4544698",
            "title": "Gold, silver slide after Trump confirms Warsh Fed chair nomination",
            "description": "<html><body><div><article data-scroll-anchor=\"true\" data-testid=\"conversation-turn-26\" data-turn=\"assistant\" data-turn-id=\"request-WEB:ef43428d-9ea4-43b5-b465-1341b504fcfa-12\" dir=\"auto\" tabindex=\"-1\"><div><div tabindex=\"-1\"><div><div data-message-author-role=\"assistant\" data-message-id=\"44a58403-f95d-494e-a568-43bad6ab2338\" data-message-model-slug=\"gpt-5-2\" dir=\"auto\"><div><div>\n<p data-eci=\"true\" data-end=\"196\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\" data-start=\"0\">Gold and silver tumbled on Friday, snapping a record-setting rally, as traders reacted to President Donald Trump’s confirmation that he will nominate Kevin Warsh as the next Federal Reserve chair.</p>\n<p data-end=\"196\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\" data-start=\"0\"><span>Spot gold (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/XAUUSD:CUR\" title=\"Gold Spot Price\">XAUUSD:CUR</a></span></span></span>) (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GLD\" title=\"SPDR® Gold Shares ETF\">GLD</a></span></span></span>) fell -4.5% at press time to $5,129.7. Silver (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/XAGUSD:CUR\" title=\"Silver Spot Price\">XAGUSD:CUR</a></span></span></span>) (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SLV\" title=\"iShares Silver Trust ETF\">SLV</a></span></span></span>) tumbled -10.3% to $103.7. A gauge of the dollar (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DXY\" title=\"US Dollar Index\">DXY</a>) climbed initially, increasing the cost of precious metals for most buyers, but has now pared its advance.</span></p>\n<p data-end=\"196\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\" data-start=\"0\"><span>Platinum (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/XPTUSD:CUR\" title=\"Platinum Spot Price\">XPTUSD:CUR</a>) -10.7% and palladium (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/XPDUSD:CUR\" title=\"Palladium Futures\">XPDUSD:CUR</a>) -8.3% also fell.</span></p>\n<p data-end=\"196\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\" data-start=\"0\"><span>Trump said on Truth Social,</span> \"I have known Kevin for a long period of time and have no doubt that he will go down as one of the<span> GREAT Fed Chairmen, maybe the best.\" </span></p>\n<p data-end=\"196\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\" data-start=\"0\"><span>The former Fed governor is known as an inflation hawk but has recently aligned with the president by publicly advocating for lower interest rates. If nominated and confirmed, he would succeed Jerome Powell, whose term at the helm ends in May.</span></p>\n<p data-end=\"196\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\" data-start=\"0\"><strong>Gold ETFs:<span> </span></strong>(<span><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GLD\" title=\"SPDR® Gold Shares ETF\">GLD</a></span>), (<span><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/IAU\" title=\"iShares Gold Trust ETF\">IAU</a></span></span></span></span>), (<span><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SGOL\" title=\"abrdn Physical Gold Shares ETF\">SGOL</a></span></span></span></span>), (<span><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/OUNZ\" title=\"VanEck Merk Gold Trust ETF\">OUNZ</a></span></span></span></span>), (<span><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BAR\" title=\"GraniteShares Gold Trust ETF\">BAR</a></span></span></span></span>), (<span><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GDX\" title=\"VanEck Gold Miners ETF\">GDX</a></span></span></span></span>), (<span><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GDXJ\" title=\"VanEck Junior Gold Miners ETF\">GDXJ</a></span></span></span></span>), (<span><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NUGT\" title=\"Direxion Daily Gold Miners Index Bull 2X Shares ETF\">NUGT</a></span></span></span></span>), (<span><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/RING\" title=\"iShares MSCI Global Gold Miners ETF\">RING</a></span></span></span></span>), and (<span><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DUST\" title=\"Direxion Daily Gold Miners Index Bear 2X Shares ETF\">DUST</a></span></span></span></span>).</p>\n<p data-end=\"196\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\" data-start=\"0\"><strong>Silver ETFs:<span> </span></strong>(<span><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SLV\" title=\"iShares Silver Trust ETF\">SLV</a></span>), (<span><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SIVR\" title=\"abrdn Physical Silver Shares ETF\">SIVR</a></span></span></span></span>), (<span><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AGQ\" title=\"ProShares Ultra Silver ETF\">AGQ</a></span></span></span></span>), (<span><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ZSL\" title=\"ProShares UltraShort Silver ETF\">ZSL</a></span></span></span></span>), (<span><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PSLV\" title=\"Sprott Physical Silver Trust\">PSLV</a></span></span></span></span>), (<span><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SIL\" title=\"Global X Silver Miners ETF\">SIL</a></span></span></span></span>), (<span><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SILJ\" title=\"Amplify Junior Silver Miners ETF\">SILJ</a></span></span></span></span>), (<span><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SLVP\" title=\"iShares MSCI Global Silver and Metals Miners ETF\">SLVP</a></span></span></span></span>).</p>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div></article></div>\n<div class=\"signup_widget_placeholder\"></div>\n</body></html>",
