            "title": "Nexstar Media declares $1.86 dividend",
            "description": "<html><body><ul>\n<li>Nexstar Media (NXST) declares <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20382287-nexstar-media-group-declares-quarterly-cash-dividend-of-1_86-per-share\" target=\"_blank\">$1.86/share quarterly dividend</a>, in line with previous.</li>\n<li>\n<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NXST/dividends/yield?source=news_bullet\">Forward yield</a> 3.59%</li>\n<li>Payable Feb. 27; for shareholders of record Feb. 13; ex-div Feb. 13.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NXST/dividends?source=news_bullet\">See NXST Dividend Scorecard, Yield Chart, &amp; Dividend Growth.</a></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"signup_widget_placeholder\"></div>\n</body></html>",
